title: MisterMusic Show 408 - indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 408 [120 minutes]  192 kbps MP3 stereo-



The MisterMusic Show brings you an eclectic mix of indie, alternative, and rock music spanning over 5 decades of hits.
New tunes from Stone Roses, Richard Ashcroft, and The Zephyr Bones on the show this week.
We travel back to May 1995 in the 'Oldie Of The Week' segment, for a hit that remained number 1 for four weeks on the Modern Rock chart in America.  It also was number 1 on the Billboard Hot 100 for three weeks that year.

The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

For recorded podcasts of the MisterMusic show, visit his podcast page-  
http://mistermusicshow.com/ . Shows are updated there first every Sunday.
Or you can google search mistermusicshow (spelled as one word) and you'll find it.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

MisterMusic is also a presenter on PodCloud1. The website that gives you shorter music segments and themes...easier 
to enjoy in the hectic schedules of today. Check it out- PodCloud1 'The One for Great Music' http://podcloud1.com/
